- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with the optimization of agent behavior. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is relevant as the paper deals with a decentralized system of agents. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the exploration of a graph, which could be seen as a robotic task.
